<div id="fullpage" class="fullpage-wrapper">
  <div id="header"><a
  href='https://www.eventbrite.com/e/40below-and-junior-achievement-presents-job-shadow-syracuse-tickets-13848929521'
  target="_blank">
    Interested in learning more? Come to our launch event at The Tech Garden
  on November 13</a></div>
  <ul id="ux-menu">
    <li>
      <a href='/businesses/new'>
    <span>Participate as a Business</span>
      </a>
    </li>
    <!--<li>
      <a href='#'>
        <span>Apply to JA Job Site</span>
      </a>
    </li>-->
  </ul>
  <ul id="menu">
    <p id="header-text"
    >Job Shadow Syracuse</p>
    <div id="menu-links">
      <li data-menuanchor="homeSlide"><a href="#homeSlide">Home</a></li>
      <li data-menuanchor="aboutSlide" ><a href="#aboutSlide">About</a></li>
      <li data-menuanchor="schoolsSlide"><a href="#schoolsSlide">Schools</a></li>
      <li data-menuanchor="businessesSlide"><a href="#businessesSlide">Businesses</a></li>
    </div>
  </ul>
  <a href='' id="event-link">Come to the Job Shadow Syracuse Expo</a>
  <div class="section" id="home" data-anchor="homeSlide">
    <div id="greeting-text">
      <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-offset-3" id="home_container">
        <div class="col-xs-6">
          <p class="lead copy-text" id="home-text">
            Job Shadow Syracuse is a collaborative effort to connect high school students
            with businesses and organizations in Syracuse, NY.

          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-6">
          <%= image_tag("40B_logo.jpeg", :width => "75%",
                        :height => "75%", :class => "img-rounded home-logo") %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="section" id="about"data-anchor="aboutSlide">
    <div class="col-xs-8 col-sm-offset-2" id="about_container">
      <div class="col-xs-3">
        <%= image_tag("in-class-1.png", :width => "50%",
                      :height => "50%", :class => "img-rounded, about-img") %>
        <p class="about-text">
          Through the Junior Achievement Job Shadow program in their high school, students
          participate in an introductory class teaching them the seven steps
          to get hired and succeed.

        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-3">
        <%= image_tag("apply-online.png", :width => "50%",
                      :height => "50%", :class => "img-rounded, about-img") %>
        <p class="about-text">
          In a second classroom session, students build on the seven steps and analyze different job
          hunting skills, which are applied through mock interviews and applications.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-3">
        <%= image_tag("job-site.png", :width => "50%",
                      :height => "50%", :class => "img-rounded, about-img") %>
        <p class="about-text">
          The students visit a local business and learn about its industry, components, and day to
          day operations.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-3">
        <%= image_tag("thank-you.png", :width => "50%",
                      :height => "50%", :class => "img-rounded, about-img") %>
        <p class="about-text">
          Following their visit students compose a thank you note
          and construct a career-preparation tool to help them find success
          in their future .
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="section" data-anchor="schoolsSlide" id="school-section">


    <div class="col-xs-8 col-sm-offset-2" id="schools-container">

      <p class="schools-text">
        Our past and present school partners include:
      </p>
      <br>
      <div class="col-xs-5">
        <ul class="schools-block">
          <li>Fowler High School</li>
          <li>Corcoran High School</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-7">
        <ul class="schools-block">
          <li>Henninger High School</li>
          <li>Nottingham High School</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>


  </div>

  <div class="section" data-anchor="businessesSlide" id="business-section">
    <div class="slide" id="business-slide-1">
      <div class="col-xs-6">
        <p class="business-text">
          There are many different reasons to participate in Job Shadow Syracuse as a Business beyond
          being listed as a sponsor.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-4 col-xs-offset-2">
        <%= image_tag("business_1.png", :class => "business-image") %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="slide">
      <div class="col-xs-6">
        <p class="business-text">
          Today's high school students are tomorrow's customers and clients,
          reach them directly by providing a positive impact on their life.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-4 col-xs-offset-2">
        <%= image_tag("business_2.png", :class => "business-image") %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="slide">
      <div class="col-xs-6">
        <p class="business-text">
          Show your employees you are committed to their commmunity and willing to go
          beyond what is required for financial success.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-4 col-xs-offset-2">
        <%= image_tag("business_3.png", :class => "business-image") %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="slide">
      <div class="col-xs-4 col-xs-offset-2">
        <p class="business-text">
          With varying levels of commitment, sign up for more information and give an opportunity to students
          who will remember your contribution the rest of their life.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-2">
        <button class="btn btn-primary btn-block"
                style="margin-top: 75%%;">Sign Up For More Information</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

